  "title": "A big star-like UFO spotted by five people in Campo Mourão [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/17/a-big-star-like-ufo-spotted-by-five-people-in-campo-mourao-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-ux",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JULY 7th, 1999</strong>. Time: 8:00 pm. In Campo Mourão, State of Paraná, five people observed a big star-like UFO, with colors varying between orange and yellow. According to the witnesses, the unidentified flying object remained stationary in the western direction for the entire period of  the sighting, about 40km away from the observers. The weather conditions were good and the communication to report the sighting to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command] was made at the time of the event.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.553. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Campo Mourão, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
